OL,7,FA police officer who deliberately
OL,8,Fweighed down keys on her laptop to
OL,9,Fmake it look like she was working has
OL,10,Fbeen dismissed without notice.
OL,12,FSomerset-based Detective Constable
OL,13,FPhilippa Baskwill was caught out when
OL,14,Fmonitoring software identified an
OL,15,Fabnormal number of keystrokes over
OL,16,Fprolonged periods of time.
