OL,5,Cworking
OL,7,FThis prompted an investigation and
OL,8,Fevidence was found showing that DC
OL,9,FBaskwill opened documents and
OL,10,Frepeatedly pressed specific keys to
OL,11,Fmake it appear as if she was working.
OL,13,FShe is barred from policing and other
OL,14,Flaw enforcement agencies following an
OL,15,Faccelerated misconduct hearing, held
OL,16,Fin front of Chief Constable Sarah Crew
OL,17,Fon Thursday 10 April.
