OL,5,Cworking
OL,7,FThe officer admitted to using her
OL,8,Fmobile phone to depress keys and
OL,9,Fprevent her laptop from going into
OL,10,Fstandby.
OL,12,FAvon and Somerset Police said the
OL,13,Fbehaviour was identified on 17
OL,14,Fseparate days in 2023, varying from a
OL,15,Ffew minutes to up to more than four
OL,16,Fhours.
OL,18,FA total of more than 21 million
OL,19,Fkeystrokes were recorded in 2023, with
OL,20,Falmost three million in one month
OL,21,Falone.
