OL,7,FOnline shopping
OL,9,FThe investigation also found evidence
OL,10,FDC Baskwill had been using her work
OL,11,Flaptop during shifts to do online
OL,12,Fshopping and search for flights.
OL,14,FOn one occasion, she had been online
OL,15,Fshopping for more than four hours
OL,16,Fduring a single shift.
