OL,5,Cworking
OL,7,FAt the hearing, Chief Constable Sarah
OL,8,FCrew found DC Baskwill had committed
OL,9,Fgross misconduct by breaching
OL,10,FStandards of Professional Behaviour
OL,11,Frelating to honesty and integrity,
OL,12,Fduties and responsibilities, and
OL,13,Forders and instructions.
OL,15,FSupt Larisa Hunt, head of the
OL,16,FProfessional Standards Department,
OL,17,Fsaid "We know officers and staff are
OL,18,Fdealing with immense pressure and high
OL,19,Fworkloads so it's extremely
OL,20,Fdisappointing for an officer to act in
OL,21,Fthis deliberate and deceitful way.
