OL,7,F"She's let down the public primarily,
OL,8,Fbut also her colleagues too.
OL,10,F"We regularly remind line managers of
OL,11,Ftheir responsibilities to hold regular
OL,12,Fcheck-ins, one-to-ones, and reviews,
OL,13,Fto consistently monitor the wellbeing
OL,14,Fand capacity of their staff.
OL,16,F"This will also ensure any further
OL,17,Finstances like this are swiftly
OL,18,Fidentified and dealt with."
